Listen and share!! 📢📣
"If white people had as much emotional upset and reaction to racial injustice, to the taking of black lives, as we do to the taking of white property, you would not see looting or rioting. These are desperate measures." quoted from a convo w/ author Robin DiAngelo, author of White Fragility. #robindiangelo #whitefragility @michaelericdyson
I urge reading the book and viewing the entire lecture on YOUTUBE.
